    "rationale": "Thirteen credibility factors assessed; twelve meet or exceed required levels. One factor (Test conditions) falls below required level due to single-condition testing, consistent with the published Nagaraja et al. assessment. The overall credibility evidence, supported by a comprehensive literature review of analogous FEA pedicle screw studies, is judged sufficient for a Medium assurance level determination. The assessment team concludes that the FEA framework is credible for the stated COU and recommends acceptance for regulatory submission support.",
